gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 134, Jazz 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Jazz, 134-120. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded a team-high 30 points, along with four rebounds and seven assists for the Thunder, while Chet Holmgren added 16 points and eight rebounds in the victory. Keyonte George tallied a career-high 30 points for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Thunder have won back-to-back games and improve to 15-7 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 7-16.
